Grate the zest of 2 limes; squeeze juice from 1 lime. Reserve separately. Combine 2 cups water, Knorr(R) Rice SidesTM- Chicken Broccoli Rice, diced chicken, roasted garlic, black pepper, and lime zest in a pot. Bring to a boil over high heat; stir. Reduce heat and cover. Simmer over low heat until most of the water has been absorbed, about 10 minutes. Top with avocado slices, fresh parsley, and fresh lime juice to taste.